    "slug": "moving-walls-at-digimax-immap-2023",
    "title": "Moving Walls at DIGIMAX IMMAP 2023",
    "excerpt": "At Moving Walls, we're all about pushing the boundaries of “outernet” advertising. We were proud to have a presence at DIGIMAX IMMAP 2023, The Philippines premier digital marketing event where various...",
    "content": "<p>At Moving Walls, we're all about pushing the boundaries of “outernet” advertising. We were proud to have a presence at DIGIMAX IMMAP 2023, The Philippines premier digital marketing event where various stakeholders from technology, brand, and media agency sides come together to discuss the emerging trends in our industry.</p>\n<p>Participating in DIGIMAX IMMAP 2023, one of the largest digital marketing conventions in the Philippines, was a source of pride for us at Moving Walls. It was more than just an event, it was an opportunity to connect with the brightest minds in the industry, sharing our experiences and insights.</p>\n<p>The event brought together stakeholders from the technology, brand, and media agency sides to discuss emerging industry trends. At Moving Walls, we seized the chance to exchange ideas and knowledge with some of the industry's best. DIGIMAX IMMAP 2023 focused on the theme 'Empower with Entertainment,' delving into the future of digital video blockbusters, optimizing sonic engagement through digital audio and sound production, building community through meaningful connections, and navigating the whirlwind worlds of the Web3 revolution.</p>\n<p><strong>Showcasing the Strength of PDOOH</strong></p>\n<p>During DIGIMAX IMMAP 2023, we highlighted the potential of <a title=\"programmatic digital out-of-home (pDOOH)\" href=\"https://lmx.ai/p-dooh/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">programmatic digital out-of-home (pDOOH)</a> advertising. We illustrated how pDOOH delivers measurable results compared to traditional OOH advertising. At our event booth, attendees could get a first-hand demonstration of DOOH planning and measurement capabilities.</p>\n<p><strong>Elevating Event Visibility Through Sponsorship</strong></p>\n<p>As media sponsors, we amplified the event's reach. Using LED billboards along highways, we ensured that DIGIMAX IMMAP 2023 was able to build real-world awareness among potential event attendees.</p>\n<figure><img class=\"wp-image-11283\" src=\"https://stg.movingwalls.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Original-size-Feature-Images-1-1-1024x335.png\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\n<p><strong>The future is AI.</strong></p>\n<p>At DIGIMAX IMMAP 2023, AI's prominence in the media industry was a recurring theme. Embracing AI is not an option but a necessity, and Moving Walls is excited to be at the forefront of this transformative change.</p>\n<p>our journey at DIGIMAX IMMAP 2023 was a celebration of innovation, networking, and technological advancement. </p>",
