    "slug": "moving-hearts-sets-the-stage-for-2024-with-digital-wednesday",
    "title": "Moving Hearts sets the stage for 2024 with Digital Wednesday ",
    "excerpt": "The Malaysian Digital Association’s 46th instalment of the Digital Wednesday was all the rave. The event turned out to be a hive of activity with the experts from Moving Walls taking on the stage as s...",
    "content": "<p>The Malaysian Digital Association’s 46th instalment of the Digital Wednesday was all the rave. The event turned out to be a hive of activity with the experts from Moving Walls taking on the stage as sponsors to talk about the trends and developments in the ad-tech space. Our very own DOOH expert, Shyam Ravishankar, the Head of Agencies and Brands unveiled the 1+1 offer at the event. He invited all those wishing to try out DOOH for their brands to avail themselves a 1+1 offer where Moving Walls will match the DOOH investment with the inventory of the same value. The conversations had everyone engaged and entertained. The room was filled with stimulating conversations, energizing ideas and of course plenty of food to go around!</p>\n<figure><img src=\"https://stg.movingwalls.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/1-Original-size-Feature-Images-21-1-1024x335.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12892\"/></figure>",
    "category": "Industry Trends",
