    "slug": "an-exclusive-evening-of-sake-strategy-and-ooh-innovation-in-singapore",
    "title": "An Exclusive Evening of Sake, Strategy, and OOH Innovation in Singapore",
    "excerpt": "What an unforgettable evening it was in Singapore on the 6th of March 2025, at our Sake &amp; Media Strategy Event in Singapore, where 30 industry professionals gathered to explore the future of Japan...",
    "content": "<p>What an unforgettable evening it was in Singapore on the 6th of March 2025, at our Sake &amp; Media Strategy Event in Singapore, where 30 industry professionals gathered to explore the future of Japan's OOH landscape and its global impact.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The event began with an opening address by the esteemed Koichi Inaba-san, Senior Corporate Officer – Deputy Director General of Media Solution HQ, Head of Digital Signage Business Division, and Director of MASTRUM, setting the tone for a remarkable evening. This was followed by expert presentations from Takayuki Owada-san (Deputy Manager – jeki JR East) and Srikanth Ramachandran (Founder &amp; Group CEO – Moving Walls Group), who shared valuable insights into the groundbreaking innovations of MASTRUM and GLOOH (Global Out-of-Home) respectively. Special mention to Masaru Yamaguchi-san, Director – Center of Promotion – MASTRUM, whose contributions were vital for the success of the event.</p>\n<figure><img src=\"https://stg.movingwalls.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/moving-walls-jeki-team-at-sake-event-singapore.webp\" alt=\"Moving Walls and jeki Team at Sake Event Singapore\" class=\"wp-image-18351\"/></figure>\n<p>Takayuki Owada-san introduced MASTRUM, powered by Moving Walls, is an OOH platform operated by East Japan Marketing &amp; Communications (Jeki), a DSP/SSP company. MASTRUM supports not only transit advertising but also street advertising, retail media, as well as analog media such as hanging posters and outdoor sheet advertising. What makes MASTRUM truly unique is its exclusive programmatic inventory across Japan's extensive railway network and diverse venue types including retail locations and transit hubs.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The platform is seamlessly connected to leading DSPs including DV360, The Trade Desk, Stackadapt, and Mediasmart, alongside Moving Walls’ MAX; a comprehensive universal OOH planning, optimization &amp; reporting platform, and MASTRUM's own DSP, enabling advertisers to easily access and <a href=\"https://stg.movingwalls.com/market/japan/\" title=\"Billboards in Japan\">purchase premium Japanese OOH inventory</a>. Leveraging data powered by KDDI - a leading Japanese telecommunications company - along with proprietary datasets, MASTRUM offers sophisticated audience targeting capabilities and robust measurement solutions, making it the premier choice for brands looking to connect with high-traffic audiences throughout Japan.</p>\n<figure><img src=\"https://stg.movingwalls.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/srikanth-ramachandran-presented-glooh.webp\" alt=\"Srikanth Ramachandran presented GLOOH at Sake Event Singapore\" class=\"wp-image-18356\"/></figure>\n<p>Srikanth Ramachandran presented GLOOH (Global Out-of-Home), a powerful &amp; strategic initiative, designed to enable seamless, data-driven, and measurable OOH campaigns across multiple global markets. By combining real-time insights, programmatic OOH, and access to extensive digital screen inventories across key global hubs in APAC, <a href=\"https://stg.movingwalls.com/mena-inventory/\" title=\"digital signage network built for MENA\">MENA</a>, and the Americas including New York, Singapore, London, and Tokyo, GLOOH empowers brands to execute cross-border campaigns with precision and scale. With a proven track record of delivering automated and transparent advertising solutions for global brands, Moving Walls' GLOOH is revolutionizing how advertisers engage with audiences, improving media efficiency and maximizing return on investment.</p>\n<p>From China's CNY celebration campaign across Africa to Indonesia's metro lines featuring JBL's latest products from Singapore, GLOOH has powered impactful campaigns in diverse environments. In the past year alone, <a href=\"https://stg.movingwalls.com/blog/how-data-and-automation-are-transforming-ooh-media-across-africa/\" title=\"screens across Africa\">screens across Africa</a>, Southeast Asia, and the US have showcased content that proves OOH advertising's evolution beyond just location to deliver measurable global impact.</p>\n<p>With strategic hubs like Singapore, Hong Kong, and Tokyo leading this transformation, the advertising industry is embracing a borderless approach where data-driven decisions help brands achieve unprecedented visibility and engagement across markets.</p>\n<figure><img src=\"https://stg.movingwalls.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/moving-walls-and-jeki-team-sake-event-singapore.webp\" alt=\"Moving Walls and jeki Team at Sake Event Singapore\" class=\"wp-image-18361\"/></figure>\n<figure><img src=\"https://stg.movingwalls.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/moving-walls-jeki-team-sake-event-singapore.webp\" alt=\"Moving Walls and jeki Team at Sake Event Singapore\" class=\"wp-image-18366\"/></figure>\n<p><strong>What's Next?</strong><br>As the OOH landscape continues to evolve, now is the time to rethink your advertising strategy. Whether you're looking to leverage MASTRUM's exclusive programmatic inventory in Japan and expand globally with GLOOH's cross-border capabilities, we can help take your brand to the next level. <a href=\"https://stg.movingwalls.com/contact-us/\" title=\"Contact Moving Walls\">Get in touch with us today</a>!</p>",
